# Troubleshooting log

Whenever you hit an install, build, develop, test, or deploy error in this repo:

1. Check `TROUBLESHOOTING.md` first.
2. If it is a **new** error, append a section there in the same style as existing entries (heading, when it appears, terminal excerpt, numbered steps).
3. Do this in the same session — do not wait to be asked.

See also `AGENTS.md`.
